 formula2=\left\{ \begin{array}{ll} A \left( $x1 : $y1 \right) &  B  \left( $x2 : $y2 \right) \\ \angle A  =  $a ^{o} & \angle B  =  $b ^{o} \\ d(AB) \approx &  $ab \\ d(AC) \approx  & $ac \\ d(BC) \approx & $bc \\ C & \input{14}{0}{background-color:lightgreen;color:red;text-align:center}{( : )}{0} \end{array} \right. 


